Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.77,0:00:55.13,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.13,0:00:59.14,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:03.96,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.70,0:01:11.78,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:18.93,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.23,0:01:25.55,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:33.21,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Wauf, and I'm the captain of the {\i1}Messis{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy base ship that Chor Tempest discovered in Plumbish airspace...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...is still missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest has already sent out four scouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The increasing number of enemy sightings during the past twelve hours worries me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And there are only two Simoun left aboard the {\i1}Messis{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What an awful feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.27,0:02:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All sections are at general quarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dismiss the kitchen staff and have them report for duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:49.25,Titles,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Maajon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for you, I want to draw...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.40,0:03:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Emerald Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What a funny-looking face!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.55,0:03:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it looks like its owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Rodoreamon? 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Or the seamstress, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be laughing at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Busted!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Aircraft silhouettes sighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.37,0:03:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Silhouettes! Not Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine o'clock! Silhouettes! Not Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We should assume that we've been discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Aircraft sighted at six o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Decrease altitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll hit the trees if we go any lower!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter! Mow them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Find us a place to hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.35,0:04:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a hill at one o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Circle around it at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare for landing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we can fight them with just two Simoun, it's all over if the {\i1}Messis{\i0} goes down. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A baby bird that loses its mother will starve to death. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll scare the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Limone's not scared, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's our turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.73,0:04:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominura...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The Simoun are the chariots of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the plan, Dominura?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we pursue the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.24,0:05:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Defending the {\i1}Messis{\i0} is our top priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to split up and defend the approach points.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed. Let's hit the ground and use the dirt as a smokescreen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Aaeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Limone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I kinda brought Rodoreamon's stuffed toy along.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go the anchors!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.33,0:07:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, we made it... somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right: it {\i1}was{\i0} a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.93,0:07:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, they're gone. Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.54,0:07:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They just pretend to leave, then they circle back for another look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, shall we get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about surviving out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not like knowing the art of war is anything to be proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.02,0:07:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The art of war?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the art of war!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:07:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the way to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to learn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Dominura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.97,0:08:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you wanted to do it for me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Maajon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't trying to force you into anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.99,0:08:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I need to think that I'm doing it for someone else... 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.87,0:08:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...or I can't get anywhere with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand how you're feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't know why I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we're a pair, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have realized earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean we were lured out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.23,0:09:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They split up Chor Tempest to divide its strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Limone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They still haven't found our exact position.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominura...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I assume you know this already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun is going to rise soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The next attack will be able to find us quite easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what options do we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,One is to wait for the other four Simoun to return,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,hold a defensive position here, and fight off the enemy attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.22,0:10:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The other is to leave the area at once. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.36,0:10:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If we did, what would become of Neviril and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, is it your opinion that in that case, 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the chance of survival for the Simoun crews who haven't returned would be very low? 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you basing this nonsense on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest is the Theocracy's strongest choir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that it could be defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's gonna come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.59,0:10:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Paraietta!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to search for the other Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:10:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What about defending the {\i1}Messis{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only the captain's opinion that the enemy will strike again! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't know that for certain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Such dangerous foolishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Together—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Limone is my pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dominura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.14,0:11:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And I am Limone's pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What is wrong with you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be so callous?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Our friends are in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not abandon my comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Comrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you mean "Neviril?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when are you better than her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Better? How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:12:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sibylla Aurea is Chor Tempest's best sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking that she needs a nobody like you to protect her...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's damned arrogant of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.30,0:12:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Limone, we're going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have something to do first. I shall be quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,As for you, with your emotions so riled up,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,it's doubtful that you and Aaeru could make your Simoun fly, Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.31,0:13:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominura?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I'm not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who has nothing to believe in has no firm ground to stand on. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, the Holy Land and Tempus Spatium have been that belief. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.43,0:13:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.69,0:13:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The Simoun showed me something I did not want to know. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you see back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wapourif, forget about that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.86,0:13:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That is my final word.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Unidentified aircraft at eight o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They're earlier than we expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.82,0:14:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Messis{\i0} will hold position and counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaeru, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Without you, I cannot save Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominura, please take care of yourself. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And the same to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Limone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to put it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.74,0:15:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how high they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's almost like the Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.31,0:15:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Dominura!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaeru! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Falcon Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Falcon Ri Maajon, again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll do it as many times as I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the most destructive Ri Maajon we can do together?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.17,0:15:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ri Maajon of the Raging Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ri Maajon of the Raging Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.89,0:16:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They've improved a lot in a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They still can't compare with the Simoun, but with those numbers...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Fish Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.49,0:16:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it! They keep interrupting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Messis{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... now is the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But y'know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.12,0:17:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.25,0:17:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't {\i1}you{\i0} scared, Dominura?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that you know me so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What I saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It was terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It destroyed everything I believed in, everything I held dear to my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.77,0:17:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But... that's not what I'm afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.63,0:17:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What I glimpsed beyond the horror...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I am afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't really put it into words, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.66,0:17:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I had to name it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:17:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hope."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.63,0:18:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They're fighting for the {\i1}Messis{\i0}! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,For us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.95,0:18:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.07,0:18:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't let the sibyllae's prayers go to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll lure the enemy towards us and let the priestesses escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What the—?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiots! Do they have a death wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,For us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it must be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.67,0:18:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready the main battery!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dominura...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what awaits us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Emerald Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn. All this time, and we still couldn't find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait—what is this feeling?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.49,0:19:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It feels so dear to me... yet infinitely cold.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.22,0:19:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.91,0:19:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's—!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.12,0:19:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Emerald... Ri Maajon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they—?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Dominura!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Limone! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Emerald...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...? Who the heck is doing the Emerald Ri Maajon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I'm seeing this again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.22,0:19:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to hurry back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:19:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's the...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No! They'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.71,0:20:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,STOP IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Limone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dominura?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not afraid at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We're together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Together. Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, always!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't change a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, where are Dominura and Limone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, they're persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.67,0:21:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! It's the Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! They're all okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominura...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...? What's going on? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.48,0:21:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ca-Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.46,0:21:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Look up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.03,0:21:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like we're just in the nick of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting, sibyllae!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.17,0:22:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Wauf, and I'm the captain of the {\i1}Messis{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.47,0:22:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We have managed to survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.62,0:22:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...thanks to the Arcus Prima and the returning Simoun from Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.15,0:22:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,However, as for Sibylla Dominura and Sibylla Limone's Simoun... 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.07,0:22:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...we were unable to find any trace of it.
